"I definitely should have known this and that"

"They don't know I don't know enough. Those who think I do know enough, they are not aware of everything I don't know and should know...so they don't count"  

"I got this far, it was difficult, yes, but you...just do it. That was different, it is not as hard as this" 

"Someday they will find out I don't know enough and then what?"

"I don't have impostor syndrome, in my case all this is true"
speaker: SYSTEM
